Interface TagLibrary

All Superinterfaces:
AutoCloseable, Closeable
All Known Implementing Classes:
JarTldFileTagLibrary, TagDirImplicitTagLibrary, TldFileTagLibrary, WarJarTagLibrary, WarJarTldFileTagLibrary, WarTagDirImplicitTagLibrary
public interface TagLibrary extends Closeable
Base class for a tag library source. Different tag libraries will locate resources, such as tag files, in different ways.
Author:
mroth

    • getTldDocument

      Document getTldDocument(DocumentBuilder documentBuilder) throws IOException, SAXException, TransformerFactoryConfigurationError, TransformerException
      Returns a Document of the effective tag library descriptor for this tag library. This might come from a file or be implicitly generated.
      Parameters:
      documentBuilder - DocumentBuilder to obtain DOM Document for creating an XML-document.
      Returns:
      created XML-Document
      Throws:
      IOException - if an I/O error has occurred
      SAXException - If any parse errors occur.
      TransformerFactoryConfigurationError - Thrown in case of service configuration error or if the implementation is not available or cannot be instantiated.
      TransformerException - If an unrecoverable error occurs during the course of the transformation.
